snippet.title: INSPIRE - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
4 years ago I knew nothing about game development, so I'm beyond excited to share the gameplay trailer of my first game "INSPIRE", which will be released on 12-4-2024!

INSPIRE is a Stylized Top-Down Shooter set in the near future. Customize your arsenal, explore, and shoot your way through an alien invasion alongside your transformable backpack companion.

WISHLIST INSPIRE
https://linktr.ee/HusmanGames

Be the first to know all updates regarding INSPIRE:
▶ https://linktr.ee/HusmanGames

-Nick
